data.description: Motivated Seller!  Sellers FHA loan at 3.49% may be assumable with qualifying credit!!!  Country living with views galore, only 20 minutes from town!  Waiting for a buyer to bring all their animals, RV's, Toys, Trailers and/or home business! So much opportunity! Plenty of room to build a Shop, office or RV garage!  Great views of Mountains and Valleys!  Seller will consider buyer concessions, interest rate buy down, and/or flooring credits with a good offer!!!  Come see today!
